@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_sxqfip(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.exp(tmp)
    v1 = ((0.50 / (v2 + 0.66 / v2 + 0.84)) + wp.sin(wp.abs(v0 + 0.97)))
    v2 = v1
    tmp = wp.sin((wp.abs(v0 + 0.08) - wp.sin(tmp + 0.34)))
    data[tid] = v0
